    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The engine and transmission are operational, though the car shows visible signs of wear and tear. The exterior paint has some scratches and the interior upholstery is worn in several areas. Some minor mechanical maintenance may be required in the near future.",
