      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This unit has been meticulously maintained, ensuring consistent performance and long-term reliability. Featuring a refined profile and a well-appointed interior, it represents a premier acquisition for the discerning driver who demands quality and value. We invite you to experience the superior handling and engineering of this exceptional automobile.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
