    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for my trusty car! It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in really solid shape\u2014it runs beautifully and is ready for your next adventure. I've taken great care of it, and it definitely shows. If you\u2019re looking for a smooth ride that won\u2019t let you down, this is the one! Come by and take it for a spin, I\u2019d love to show it to you!",
