    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This power unit delivers an 8,400 RPM redline and utilizes individual throttle bodies for razor-sharp throttle response. The vehicle is mechanically robust, with critical preventative maintenance\u2014including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service\u2014already completed. The chassis features Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a variable M differential lock, ensuring the rear-drive dynamics remain composed under load. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its mileage, the performance envelope is fully intact, offering a visceral, analog experience for the dedicated enthusiast.",
